These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, snowmobile, scooter, roller, trike
There 6 different types of food: onion, pomegranate, cabbage, apple, avocado, carrot
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating apple is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
6. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Transport   | trike | quad-bike  | snowmobile    | scooter  | helicopter      | roller    |
| Food      | pomegranate  | carrot | avocado | onion | apple | cabbage |

