.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, sudoku, rock-climbing, fishing, dancing
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, cola, lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk, tea
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | fishing | traveling | dancing | rock-climbing     | sudoku  |
| Beverage           | lemonade | cola    | water      | tea  | soy-milk | almond-milk |

