.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, lily, bellflower, dahlia, iris
City: miami, colone, new-york, nizza, london, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
2. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Flower   | lily  | bellflower | tulip      | marigold  | iris | dahlia |
| City     | miami | san-francisco  | london | new-york | nizza  | colone    |

