.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: pink, amber, green, lavender, orange, ivory
House: art-deco, townhouse, modern, tower, cottage, colonial
 1. the modern house is the person who likes pink##1
 2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 3. the cottage house is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 4. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 9. the modern house is on the right of the tower house##1
10. the person who likes lavender is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Color         | lavender | ivory | pink | orange | amber | green  |
| House   | colonial  | tower  | modern  | art-deco | cottage      | townhouse |

