.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, white, yellow, pink, blue
House: modern, craftsman, art-deco, victorian, cape-cod, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the cape-cod house is the person who likes blue##1
6. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the art-deco house##1
7. the modern house is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
9. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Color   | blue    | white    | apricot | pink     | chestnut   | yellow     |
| House   | cape-cod | craftsman | townhouse | art-deco | victorian | modern |

