.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different games are played: scrabble, go, mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly, chess
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, july, december, may, june, november
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Game         | go       | chess     | bridge | mah-jongg | monopoly | scrabble |
| Birthday   | july | june | november | december     | september  | may       |

