5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
6. the malaysian is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is the australian##1
8. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
9. the british is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Color   | yellow    | aquamarine     | light-blue | grey | pink | ivory   |
| Nationality        | nigerian | australian | british | indonesian   | brazilian    | malaysian |

