.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
City: miami, edinburgh, venice, prague, san-francisco, new-york
6 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, pony, snake, turtle, rat
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the owner of the snake is the person traveling to prague##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| City   | san-francisco | new-york | prague    | edinburgh | venice  | miami |
| Pet     | frog    | turtle | snake | rat   | pony | ferret    |

