.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, cat, lizard, bird, dog, turtle
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, lilac, aquamarine, blood-red, azure, blue
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
8. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes black##1
9. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Pet   | cat | turtle     | dog       | lizard  | bird | pony    |
| Color     | blue  | black | lilac | blood-red | azure  | aquamarine |

 